    <string name="masterView_instructions">
        1. To scan a new certificate, hit the plus symbol in the master view. \n\n
2. Point the camera steadily at the QR code of the certificate you want to scan for a few seconds. \n\n
3. A query now opens in which the PIN assigned to the certificate must be entered. \n\n
4. If the two PINs match, you get to the detailed view of the document. \n\n
5. If you are not asked to enter the pin after the scan, the QR code was incorrect.
Faulty scans are then highlighted in red in the master view.</string>

